(Steps to fix VPN not connecting:) Tj T*
(1. Check your internet connection is working first.) Tj T*
(2. Close and fully restart the VPN client application.) Tj T*
(3. Make sure you are entering the correct VPN username and password.) Tj T*
(4. Try connecting to a different VPN server location.) Tj T*
(5. Temporarily disable your firewall or antivirus and retry.) Tj T*
(6. Uninstall and reinstall the VPN client if issue persists.) Tj T*
